          <!-- â˜… æ³¨æ„ï¼šä¹‹å‰åœ¨è¿™é‡Œçš„è‡ªå®šä¹‰æŒ‡ç¤ºå™¨ <view> å·²ç»è¢«åˆ é™¤äº†ï¼ -->
        </block>
      </view>
      
      <view class="post-meta">
        <text class="post-time">{{post.formattedCreateTime}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="vote-section">
        <view class="actions-left">
          <view class="vote-count {{post.isVoted ? 'voted' : ''}}">ğŸ‘ {{post.votes || 0}}</view>
